        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Lin Lu Xiao, a skilled firefighter, leads the Special Operations Station in Beixun City. He becomes an instructor for a reality show about firefighting and meets Nan Chu, a dancer he rescued years ago. Though they develop feelings for each other, Lin Lu Xiao hesitates due to the dangers of his job. Along with a team of new and returning firefighters, they handle emergencies like fires and earthquakes, including a major forest\n\nfire, working together to protect the city.",
